{"tid":1555833,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[集思廣益] 全正面運動。爆買日","createTime":"2019-09-09T13:29:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T04:58:07.000Z","uid":1992,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"74fd55d9e861f8a7f0e87d5c8c362609ead75490","tid":1555833,"uid":1992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T13:29:05.000Z","msg":"對家不斷宣傳示威者係破壞分子<br />\n好多運動都比有心人借題發揮<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">今次我要一粒子彈都唔比對家</span></span><br />\n我更加想證明連登仔有能力推翻畸形社之餘<br />\n更加有能力創造理想、平衡既社會<br />\n-------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1. 爆買日</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n網上已有各大黃藍商戶之地圖，我地唔會杯葛藍店，人人都有選擇光顧／不光顧的自由<br />\n但係依一日連登仔選擇買爆黃店<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">務求買到冇貨落閘為止！</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n初步諗法，二百萬人分開3-6條戰線，全日於各黃店排隊購物，比政府睇到，有良心既商店係會得到應有既回報！<br />\n<br />\n同時，令社會大眾睇到<br />\n政府不斷暴力鎮壓先係令市場蕭條，萎縮既主因<br />\n黑警打人，黨鐵封站先係導致生意清淡既元兇<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/h03FWEx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh03FWEx.jpg&h=0071aeec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n戰線。一 [港島區]<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VR86Srv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVR86Srv.jpg&h=d7123963&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LKfkWTa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLKfkWTa.jpg&h=b81b09f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n戰線。二[油尖旺]<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Raoe1j4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRaoe1j4.jpg&h=7400ce8b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ym51Gj5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fym51Gj5.jpg&h=4530ddcf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n戰線。三[元天屯]<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JzCzgUh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJzCzgUh.jpg&h=151b4c59&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W1AMSsD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW1AMSsD.jpg&h=4d574014&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n黃藍商店詳情：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/ReclaimHK/photos/a.101043784608531/101044147941828?type=3&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FReclaimHK%2Fphotos%2Fa.101043784608531%2F101044147941828%3Ftype%3D3%26sfns%3Dmo&d=8Se%2B9W40ah4Gl3auq3G%2Bullsl4SrcEEyWLual4COuMU%3D&h=c7f4113a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/ReclaimHK/photos/a.101043784608531/101044147941828?type=3&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n1. 所有商戶都加了資料來源 （網址、圖片、描述）佐證，有最基本的factcheck，可信與否自行判斷<br />\n2. 綠色商戶為有發出聲明澄清 / 具爭議性 / 疑似被擺上枱，可信與否自行判斷<br />\n3. 如是老闆或該店官方專頁發表評論，則所有旗下分店也會被加至此地圖，如言論只由某員工/分店發表，也只會加該分店資料<br />\n4. 本地圖只針對有於反送中運動明示/暗示表過態的商戶，若某些商戶是紅底/黃底但未有就反送中運動表過態，則暫時不會羅列於此"},{"pid":"81dbcfcf7d7727f457bda8af71ee205417ec7dc9","tid":1555833,"uid":1992,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T13:30:15.000Z","msg":"睇返排版一般，不過都要推十連<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bab06a91c2b72453f89cfe167b520d4ab5f259e3","tid":1555833,"uid":1992,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T13:30:31.000Z","msg":"十連<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8587540a3d74ef095508add86e3ad8d89a38ca0a","tid":1555833,"uid":1992,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T13:30:46.000Z","msg":"十連<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25d34fe4d828f845c71d8d358d2f4fbeb1e268e6","tid":1555833,"uid":164420,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T13:30:55.000Z","msg":"推，和理非能夠做到"},{"pid":"192fccaa7310f134a09d8bfe796ad1bf605e0d3b","tid":155